New Job Assignment
==================

Hi <%= vendor.firstName || vendor.email %>,

<%= assignedBy.firstName || assignedBy.email %> has assigned you a maintenance request.
Please accept or decline within 24 hours.

JOB DETAILS
-----------
Reference #:    <%= request.mruid %>
Title:          <%= request.title %>
Description:    <%= request.description %>
Category:       <%= request.category.replace(/_/g, ' ') %>
Priority:       <%= request.priority.toUpperCase() %>
Property Entry: <%= request.permissionToEnter ? 'Permission granted' : 'Must coordinate with resident' %>
<% if (request.scheduledDate) { %>Scheduled Date: <%= new Date(request.scheduledDate).toLocaleDateString() %>
<% } %><% if (request.estimatedCost) { %>Estimated Cost: $<%= (request.estimatedCost / 100).toFixed(2) %>
<% } %><% if (request.preferredDate) { %>Resident Preferred Date: <%= new Date(request.preferredDate).toLocaleDateString() %>
<% } %><% if (request.availabilityWindows && request.availabilityWindows.length > 0) { %>Resident Availability: <%= request.availabilityWindows.join(', ').replace(/_/g, ' ') %>
<% } %>
Log in to the portal to accept or decline this assignment.

Questions? Contact <%= assignedBy.firstName || assignedBy.email %><% if (assignedBy.email) { %> at <%= assignedBy.email %><% } %>.

